{"commands": [{"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "\n%md-sandbox\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 0; padding-top: 9px;\">\n  <img src=\"https://databricks.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/db-academy-rgb-1200px.png\" alt=\"Databricks Learning\" style=\"width: 1200px\">\n</div>", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "e67b6dc8-8090-4562-911c-1ba7f86180bf", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "061c1b44-2bc7-491a-b5df-a1986d01e7f2", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 1, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md-sandbox\n<img src=\"https://files.training.databricks.com/images/Apache-Spark-Logo_TM_200px.png\" style=\"float: left: margin: 20px\"/>\n\n# Silver To Gold - Winning Investors\n\nIn this notebook we are going to find out who were the top 10 highest earning investor. Let's get started!\n\n## In this exercise you will:\n* Practice joins, aggregations, ordering and limiting DataFrames\n\n## Prerequisites\n* Web browser: **Chrome**\n* A cluster configured with **8 cores** and **DBR 7.0**", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "b58a8982-ab9b-466d-8d7e-736a182321ca", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "afa1013b-0e9c-4bce-a12c-41c563df8296", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 2, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n## ![Spark Logo Tiny](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png) Classroom-Setup<br>\n\nFor each lesson to execute correctly, please make sure to run the **`Classroom-Setup`** cell at the start of each lesson (see the next cell) and the **`Classroom-Cleanup`** cell at the end of each lesson.", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "b336ade6-d1c5-42dd-85e7-78b9b9bcec45", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "d4f2e36c-be88-463b-80bf-52a9019bf808", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 3, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%run ./Includes/PCF-17G-ClassroomSetup", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "db0e689f-3121-439c-a0b1-957619633f04", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "b96a23ca-6a73-4dc5-9740-ca92418582d2", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 4, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n## ![Spark Logo Tiny](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png) Steps to Complete<br>\n\nFor each lesson to execute correctly, please make sure to run the **`Classroom-Setup`** cell at the start of each lesson (see next cell) and the **`Classroom-Cleanup`** cell at the end of each lesson.\nImplement the **`challenge()`** function to achieve the following:\n* Read the **`investorsPath`** into a DataFrame and select the **`investor_id`** and **`name`** columns.\n* Read **`stockTransactionsPath`** to a DataFrame.\n* Left join **`stockTransactions`** and **`investors`**.\n* Select the **`investor`**, **`name`**, **`spend_balance`** columns and cast the **`order_timestamp`** column to date and rename it **`date`**.\n* Group bz the **`date`**, **`investor`** and **`name`** columns.\n* Aggregate the sum of the **`spend_balance`** column, round and rename it **`daily_win`**.\n* Sort **`daily_win`** in descending order.\n* Keep only the top 10 records.\n* Write the result to **`targetDirectory`** as a Delta table using the overwrite mode.\n* Return the joined DataFrame.\n\nThe schema of the resulting DataFrame should look like this:\n  \n|name|type|\n|---|---|\n|date|DateType|\n|investor|LongType|\n|name|StringType|\n|daily_win|DoubleType|", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "58397214-bb73-4ecb-9271-299df83b7dc5", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "bcd4537f-d507-429c-b6e5-03e6d1f1ef85", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 5, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "// ANSWER\n\ndef solution(spark:org.apache.spark.sql.SparkSession, investorsPath:String, stockTransactionsPath:String, targetDirectory:String) : DataFrame = {\n  import org.apache.spark.sql.functions._\n\n  //   Read the `investorsPath` into a DataFrame and select the `\"investor_id\"` and `\"name\"` columns.\n  val investors = (spark.read.format(\"delta\").load(investorsPath).select(\"investor_id\",\"name\"))\n  \n  //   Read to `\"stockTransactionsPath\"` to a DataFrame.\n  val stockTransactions = (spark.read.format(\"delta\").load(stockTransactionsPath))\n  \n  \n  //   Left join `stockTransactions` and `investors` where the \"investor_id\" equals \"investor\".\n  //   Select the \"investor\", \"name\", \"spend_balance\" columns and cast the `order_timestamp` column to date and rename it date.\n  //   Group by \"date\", \"investor\", \"name\" columns.\n  //   Aggregate the sum of the `spend_balance` column and rename it `daily_win`.\n  //   Sort `daily_win` in descending order.\n  //   Limit the result count to 10.\n  val investorsJoined = (stockTransactions.join(investors, (investors(\"investor_id\") === stockTransactions(\"investor\")), \"left\")\n         .select($\"investor\", $\"name\", $\"spend_balance\", $\"order_timestamp\".cast(\"date\").alias(\"date\"))\n         .groupBy(\"date\", \"investor\", \"name\")\n         .agg(round(sum(\"spend_balance\")).alias(\"daily_win\"))\n         .orderBy(desc(\"daily_win\"))\n         .limit(10)\n         )\n  \n  //   Write the result to `targetDirectory` as a Delta table using the overwrite mode.\n  investorsJoined.write.mode(\"overwrite\").format(\"delta\").option(\"overwriteSchema\", \"true\").save(targetDirectory)\n  \n  //   Return the joined DataFrame.\n  return investorsJoined\n}\n\nval finalDF = solution(spark, investorsPath, stockTransactionsPath, targetDirectory)\ndisplay(finalDF)", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "ba61c113-a7c3-4a48-9cbb-b92f769d9fbe", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "da668db5-d2d0-4f31-8966-4958bfc26cb6", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 6, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n<h2><img src=\"